initialize

public static void initialize(String cep)
This MUST be called when your application starts to initialize the client If the cep is null then a grid is started within the client JVM to host the grid servers locally. This is useful for debugging

Parameters:
cep - The catalog service end points (h:p,h:p,h:p)
